<h1>InterForm Actor Test Page</h1>

<hr><!-- Standard header for if_demo files -->
&lt;<b>URL:</b> <a href="&url;">&url;</a>&gt;<br>
<b>Source:</b> <a href="/PIA/Agents/&agentName;/&fileName;">&fileName;</a>
