<h3>Useful Information:</h3>
<ul>
  <li> <a href=/&agentName;/actors.if>list defined InterForm Actors</a>
  <li> <a href=/Agency/agents.if>list running PIA agents</a>
  <li> <a href=/&agentName;/entities.if>list defined entities</a>
  <li> <a href=/&agentName;/options.if>view/change options</a>
  <li> <a href=/Agency/debug.if>toggle debugging</a> (currently 
       <code language="perl"> $main::debugging? "on" : "off"; </code> );
